assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Zhejiang Jinggong Integration Technology Co., Ltd. researches, develops, produces, and sells solar photovoltaic equipment, carbon fiber composite equipment, new building energy-saving equipment, textile special equipment, and robot intelligence equipment in China and internationally. The company provides photovoltaic equipment, including polysilicon ingot furnaces and squarers, and diamond wire slicing machines. It also offers building materials comprising PU/mineral wool/PIR sandwich panel lines, HVM double-deck high speed roll forming machines, HL-310-type fence board production lines, JZW digital control folders, XBJ type of sandwich composite production lines, and down pipe forming and curving pipe machines, as well as high speed tile, roll, purlin, and floor deck forming machines. In addition, it provides textile equipment, such as JGT1000 series and winders, as well as fancy twisting, rotor spinning, double twisting, and coated wire machines; and precision manufacturing, complete equipment, and special parts manufacturing equipment. Further, the company offers robot intelligent equipment; server cabinets, cold channel closed systems, modular data centers, and electrical control cabinets; and chemical process technology and equipment, exhaust gas treatment systems, material and energy recovery technology and equipment, pressure vessel design and manufacturing equipment. The company was formerly known as Zhejiang Jinggong Science & Technology Co., Ltd and changed its name to Zhejiang Jinggong Integration Technology Co., Ltd. in March 2023. Zhejiang Jinggong Integration Technology Co., Ltd. was founded in 1968 and is based in Shaoxing, China.
